Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.52,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勝利掴むまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:53.06,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One pedal for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.61,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たどり着くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:57.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}踏み込み続けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2050B9&\bord3}奇蹟終有一天會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:58.26,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2050B9&\bord3}我總是抱著這種期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:01.19,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HCA8139&\bord3}其實對自己的放縱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.27,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HCA8139&\bord3}終究會自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.97,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H7B54CB&\bord3}有限的時間緊追在身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.53,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H7B54CB&\bord3}質問著我 這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:12.24,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H46B3CD&\bord3}糾結於不足之處的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:13.63,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H46B3CD&\bord3}已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:18.41,ED_CH,,0,0,5,,{\3c&H63AE5D&\bord3}之所以低著頭前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:22.28,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是為了步伐更加有力
Comment: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:23.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Override!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:28.54,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超越臨界點 聲音消失的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:33.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感受到心跳越來越快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:38.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已下定決心 只需讓希望燃起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:44.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前進 不斷前進 已經沒有回頭路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:47.79,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到衝過終點線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.52,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿下勝利為止
Comment: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:53.06,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One pedal for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.61,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抵達目標之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:57.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會不斷地踩下去
